@startuml
start

:Extract 10 years of legacy enquiry, feedback, citizen, and file data;
:Profile source data for volume, quality, duplicates, missing channels, and file references;
:Map records to Contact, Case, ContentVersion, ContentDocumentLink, and Migration_Batch__c;
:Cleanse and deduplicate citizens using phone, email, and MDM/citizen ID where available;
:Load reference data, users, roles, queues, divisions, and metadata;
:Pilot load representative sample and reconcile counts;

if (Pilot accepted?) then (Yes)
  :Bulk load 6M historical Case records in controlled batches;
  :Upload 100GB historical files as Salesforce Files or approved archive links;
  :Reconcile record counts, file links, ownership, sharing, and audit fields;
  :Freeze legacy writes and perform delta migration;
else (No)
  :Fix mapping, cleansing, or storage approach;
  stop
endif

:Post-migration validation, report certification, and rollback checkpoint;
:Cut over citizen contact channels to Salesforce;

stop
@enduml
